":"2019-11-11T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ca05967b136d7cd280411accefff6725574336","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3662efb18113cb7bcb9d617ca9c45d91ff5d8e80","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a66b51ab9b0da0e15180ab574a74032ece33ce8","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"【手動轉】<br />\n<br />\n聖十字架堂陳玉強執事聲稱警察有權進入教堂執法，因而放警察進入教堂範圍拘捕青年，令人髮指震驚。<br />\n<br />\n陳執事明顯違反教區機制，並無通知主教及法律顧問。教區必須嚴正交代。<br />\n<br />\n有教友女士指出堂方承諾會開放教堂，直斥執事違反機制，質問執事如何對得起天主教徒。<br />\n<br />\n教區、堂方主任司鐸梁達材神父和陳執事如果不公開道歉、為被捕青年提供法律支援，並給予公眾合理交代，我呼籲教友杯葛所有教堂活動。<br />\n<br />\n教堂本來應該是保護羊群的地方，卻成為國家鎮壓人民的幫兇，恥與為伍。<br />\n<br />\n「若是你的右眼使你跌倒，剜出它來，從你身上扔掉，因為喪失你一個肢體，比你全身投入地獄裡，為你更好。」（瑪：五29）"},{"pid":"afcb00e2782d1b0f75289859f5c92f09430688dc","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"教友已經做緊嘢請不要裝修教堂<br />\n唔介意你哋裝修佢本人"},{"pid":"4807e924c9e5b8b3d27951742bde0fdfbb93c9d3","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a66b51ab9b0da0e15180ab574a74032ece33ce8","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"【手動轉】<br />\n<br />\n聖十字架堂陳玉強執事聲稱警察有權進