06","tid":1707032,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351d567d729e80b5e00477fff0957163d37a3939","tid":1707032,"uid":300013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f771b572fcf0b637c7207befb481e0e6d2f89444","tid":1707032,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"執事地位高過牧師的，銅鑼灣果間教會都係因為海外同香港執事既壓力，<br />\n所以而家銅鑼灣有示威活動時會關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"執事係天主教。牧師係基督教。聖十字堂係天主教。何來執事高過牧師？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好扮代表啦，唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"我之前以為果間係基督教教會黎，基督教黎講執事/長老 係高過牧師。<br />\n<br />\n天主教我唔識"},{"pid":"7639e1a2000b2e72d1bc2b82b8b47074f5ab13f8","tid":1707032,"uid":298759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f771b572fcf0b637c7207befb481e0e6d2f89444","tid":1707032,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"執事地位高過牧師的，銅鑼灣果間教會都係因為海外同香港執事既壓力，<br />\n所以而家銅鑼灣有示威活動時會關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"1.聖十字堂係天主教，有神父，冇牧師<br />\n2.執事都有分階級，目前未知呢個人係咩階，不過佢係終身執事可以視為此會內最高（雖然最高都可能有幾個人）<br />\n3.一般黎講神父地位仍然高於執事，但目前似乎唔少地方缺乏神父，就變左終身執事最高<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人信仰新教，純個人研究可能有錯"},{"pid":"c58ce437f003be0eea5ceb854a05cf30a16e9960","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908593f0d26200de03dd541ea28d71c1fa0231fd","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-