b48","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7449a12dca094efb4fd02826dfcef393f8222b6f","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c706abf6bba6512f1366a8e868b86c731c7fd89","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKunFJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKunFJ6.jpg&h=9370c9c9&s={SIZE}\" />聖堂神父同個執事割左"},{"pid":"b809c7ad541a6469125c8e5780477d0f4e0faca6","tid":1707032,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c706abf6bba6512f1366a8e868b86c731c7fd89","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKunFJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKunFJ6.jpg&h=9370c9c9&s={SIZE}\" />聖堂神父同個執事割左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"有啲教堂/教會係藍，小心"},{"pid":"b7e7b858a136830abfa60a71cd204007745e0f49","tid":1707032,"uid":9260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgEiYwc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgEiYwc.jpg&h=efda3dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但你睇下教區果副死人官腔<br />\n「教堂無法保障進入期內的人士不依法被捕」<br />\n嘩你憑乜嘢話popo依法拘捕<br />\n你係法官定係天主<br />\n有邊隻眼睇到popo依法啊"},{"pid":"5136c2cb02094330ee59d9cc0198888ac25bba70","tid":1707032,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dcc18eaf63a6ae7cba818564b51e7add0d14efd","tid":1707032,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日喺成安街推進緊嘅時候<br />\n有啲手足一路向上跑<br />\n跑到上去聖十字堂嗰度就入咗去<br />\n陳玉強執事放咗班狗入去<br />\n跟住捉走左啲手足<br />\n話會送手足上白車叫我地讓路<br />\n跟住一籠車嚟咗 塔撚晒成班手足上去<br />\n屌你老母信教信撚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日點半鐘入聖十字堂祈禱，在聖堂門口企咗隻便衣狗，見到我進入門口，立即問我：你來做乜嘢（狂吼）。我跟佢講：我入去做乜你要跟住我做乜，好唔好。我會逗留約30分鐘，有無時間呀？<br />\n再問條便衣狗，你滿意嗎？唔係樣樣要話畀你知，在宗教地方要有禮貌㗎。</span>"}]}